high_descs: Walk straight then turn to the counter your left beside the stove
Pick up the kettle on the counter
Turn to your right move forward then turn left face the sink
Put the kettle on the sink and rinse it
Turn to your right then walk towards the  counter beside coffee maker
Put the kettle beside the left side of the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put the clean kettle on the counter beside the coffee maker

high_descs: Go forward past stove. Turn left to face counter.
Turn to the right and go to sink. Face sink.
Place kettle in right side of sink. Turn water on. Remove kettle from sink.
Turn to the right. Go straight. Turn right to face counter.
Place kettle on counter to the left of coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Get kettle from counter, fill with water, put kettle on counter by coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk forward slightly and turn left towards the kettle on the counter top.
Pick up the kettle from the counter top.
Turn right and walk to the sink.
Put the kettle in the sink, rinse it off, and take it out of the sink.
Turn right and walk to the coffee machine on the counter.
Put the kettle on the counter top, in front of and to the left of the coffee machine.
anns.task_desc: Place a cleaned kettle on a counter top.
